§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Given a square matrix $A ∈ 𝗥^{n × n}$.
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ ∑_{σ ∈ S_n} \left( \sgn(σ) ∏_{i = 1}^{n} a_{i,σ_{i}}
        \right) ⦉
    ⦉⦉

  ‖ We denote the determinant of $A$ by $\det A$. ⦉
